Quickstrike:




Quickstrike turned his head back. There were a few more bots behind 
him. A little bit of a larger group. He saw that Black Arachnia was 
in that group. He slowed up. If he needed to talk to her, he needed 
to make sure she was in his sights. But something else bit at him. 
Megatron was there.
